                     <h1 class="" style="text-align: center;" >WHY DTU?</h1>

                     <h3 class="intro-sub-title" >Students</h3>
                     <!-- <h2 class="intro-title">Prof. Jai Prakash Saini
                        <h4> Vice Chancellor </h4>
